OL,3,CExam board faces fine after hundreds
OL,4,Cof students given wrong GCSE results
OL,6,FAn exam board is to be fined #350,000
OL,7,Ffor breaching rules which led to
OL,8,Fhundreds of students being given the
OL,9,Fwrong GCSE grades.
OL,11,FMore than 1,500 students who had taken
OL,12,Fa WJEC food preparation and nutrition
OL,13,FGCSE in England last year were given
OL,14,Fan incorrect result.
OL,16,FWJEC is Wales' largest awarding body,
OL,17,Fbut also offers qualifications across
OL,18,FEngland and Northern Ireland.
