OL,3,CExam board faces fine after hundreds
OL,4,Cof students given wrong GCSE results
OL,6,FOfqual, England's exam watchdog, said
OL,7,FWJEC had failed to adjust teachers'
OL,8,Fmarking of coursework ` which made up
OL,9,F50% of the qualification ` to ensure
OL,10,Fresults were in line with national
OL,11,Fstandards.
OL,13,FIt meant that 847 students received
OL,14,Flower grades and 680 got higher grades
OL,15,Fthan they should have.
OL,17,FThose who received the incorrect lower
OL,18,Fgrades were given the corrected grade
OL,19,Fseveral months later, but those who
OL,20,Freceived the incorrect higher grades
OL,21,Fkept them, the watchdog confirmed.
