OL,6,FOfqual said the proposed fine reflects
OL,7,Fthe "serious nature of WJEC's
OL,8,Ffailures."
OL,10,FAmanda Swann, Ofqual's Executive
OL,11,FDirector for General Qualifications,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Students must be able to trust
OL,13,Fthat their results accurately reflect
OL,14,Ftheir performance, and what they know,
OL,15,Funderstand and can do.
