OL,6,F"These proposed fines reflect the
OL,7,Fserious nature of WJEC's failures and
OL,8,Four commitment to protecting the
OL,9,Finterests of students and maintaining
OL,10,Fthe integrity of our qualifications
OL,11,Fsystem. This includes the requirement
OL,12,Fthat GCSE, AS and A levels students
OL,13,Fare entitled to an independent review
OL,14,Fof their exam marks."
OL,16,FThe watchdog said it took into account
OL,17,Fthat WJEC had admitted the breaches,
OL,18,Faccepted responsibility, and taken
OL,19,Fsteps to prevent the problems
OL,20,Fhappening again.
